</emphasis>
<number id="3DB57E00CD26783D1CF28DB9FD0AF6EC" box="[675,703,1500,1522]" pageId="5" pageNumber="123" value="36.0">36</number>
. Pygofer, lateral view; 
<number id="3DB57E00CD26783D1DFC8DB9FC7CF6EC" box="[941,969,1500,1522]" pageId="5" pageNumber="123" value="37.0">37</number>
. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 
<number id="3DB57E00CD26783D1B2D8DB9FA2DF6EC" box="[1404,1432,1500,1522]" pageId="5" pageNumber="123" value="38.0">38</number>
. Style, ventral view; 
