. Aedeagus, ventral view; 
<number id="3DB57E00CD26783D1CD58D9FFD15F50E" box="[644,672,1530,1552]" pageId="5" pageNumber="123" value="40.0">40</number>
. Aedeagus, lateral view; 
<number id="3DB57E00CD26783D1DCF8D9FFC0FF50E" box="[926,954,1530,1552]" pageId="5" pageNumber="123" value="41.0">41</number>
. Connective, ventral view.
</paragraph>
